In accordance with AP / SIN / CLN / 687 / 2010 / M-I, Valenzuela Sandoval was arrested by Mexican Army agents on 7 June 2010 during a surveillance operation in Cipriano Valdez Street, ahead of number 80 in El Castillo, Navolato.
