The remains of pilot Bacio Cortés, born in Saltillo, arrived (incinerated) at 18: 05 hours to be handed over by the funeral to the members of the Mexican Air Force, led by Major Jaime Martinez, on the esplanade of the group, where he was expected by his family, including his daughter Amanda and his wife Cristina, his mother, brothers and other parents, students and masters.
