What is fraud at sick leave?
After the benefits, the UMP and the government launch the offensive on sick stoppages.
Nicolas Sarkozy will be in Bordeaux on Tuesday 15 November to visit a family allowance fund, and deliver a speech on the theme - recurrent since 2007 - of the fight against social fraud and assistance.
